	<!--RandomToNull-->
	<PangaeaSetting_RandomResourceToNullName>Assign random to null resources</PangaeaSetting_RandomResourceToNullName>
	<PangaeaSetting_RandomResourceToNullDescription>If a fossil or DNA has nothing assigned to it (for example, a mod was removed mid-game), assign a random one. This will avoid missing textures and useless resources, but means you may get resources you never had before.</PangaeaSetting_RandomResourceToNullDescription>
	<!--UIConsiderStockpiled-->
	<PangaeaSetting_UIConsiderStockpiledName>Bill UI considers only stockpiled</PangaeaSetting_UIConsiderStockpiledName>
	<PangaeaSetting_UIConsiderStockpiledDescription>The UI for bill configuration only accounts for resources in stockpiles, just like the UI for vanilla recipes. Disabling this makes the UI count the items in the entire map, which may lead to lower performance.</PangaeaSetting_UIConsiderStockpiledDescription>
	
